{"id":83552,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/83552","type":2,"name":"ピーターパンの冒険","name_cn":"彼得潘的冒险","summary":"      世界名作剧场系列第15部动画作品，改编自英国作家詹姆斯·马修·巴利的作品《彼得潘》（Peter Pan）。\r\n　　在达令家的3个孩子进入梦乡，绝不想长大的永远的孩子，彼得潘来临了。孩子们醒来了，与彼得潘一起从窗户出去。全体一起自由自在的飞翔。彼得潘带温蒂他们去永无岛。永无岛是什么都能做的梦想的王国。有海盗还有印第安人。温蒂在彼得潘与孩子们中是扮演妈妈的角色。刚开始叮卡贝儿(小叮当)非常忌妒温蒂，但后来她打开了心防。巨大的机械与造成骚动的海盗虎克篇，接下来是独创的魔女达克妮丝篇，彼得潘的魅力就此发展。\r\n      到第22集为止是前篇的部份，内容依著原作描写在永无岛的生活与海盗们的战斗“虎克船长篇”，第23集开始以原作没有的独创内容所展开的“达克妮丝篇”。","eps":[{"id":318606,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318606","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318607,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318607","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318608,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318608","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318609,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318609","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318610,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318610","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318611,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318611","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318612,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318612","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318613,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318613","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318614,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318614","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318615,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/318615","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":318616,"url":"http://bgm.t